casebody.data:
No. 8,

Original.

Ex parte: In the Matter of Athanasi Nicola, Petitioner. Argued November 28, 1910. Decided December 5, 1910. Mr. Lon O. Hocker, Mr. J. J. Darlington and Mr. James C. Jones for petitioner. Mr. Tyson S. Dines and Mr. Millard F. Watts for respondent.

Petition for a writ of mandamus denied, rule discharged, and petition dismissed, on authority of Tobin, Petitioner, 214 U. S. 507.
